mkdocs_pandoc is a library of preprocessors that convert mkdocs style markdown (multiple files, with the document structure defined in the mkdocs configuration file mkdocs.yml) into a single markdown document digestible by pandoc. It ships with the command line frontend tool mkdocs2pandoc as its primary user interface.

